Titolo: Higanjima

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Higanjima (Japanese: 彼岸島, lit. "Island of Paramita") is a Japanese manga series by Kōji Matsumoto. It was adapted into a live action film in 2010. It also spawned two spin-off series, Higanjima: Saigo no 47 Nichikan, and Higanjima 48 Nichigo…, both published in Kodansha's Weekly Young Magazine.